title: Maksim Tishchenko
text:
Maksim Viktorovich Tishchenko (; ; born 30 August 1974) is a Russian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> coach and a former player. He also holds <a href="Ukraine">Ukrainian</a> citizenship.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> in 1996 for <a href="FC%20Rotor%20Volgograd">FC Rotor Volgograd</a>.
European competition history.
All with <a href="FC%20Rotor%20Volgograd">FC Rotor Volgograd</a>.
